    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're driving away on a forest road, late at night, under a heavy storm. Your car breaks down. Luckily, there might be a gas station nearby. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But a misfortune never comes alone. The storm has brought something else, something otherworldly that oddly smells of spilled diesel oil. When it rains, it pours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AUTO-CRISIS</strong> is a <strong>short horror game (~60mn) </strong>about cars, rain, being lost, and bad days.   <br><br><u>WHAT TO EXPECT ?</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short psychological horror game (around 60 minutes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unreliable player character with a mystery to solve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An atmospheric game, at night, under the rain (best played with a headset!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A surreal trip about trauma, carcentrism and survivor's guilt</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>WHAT <strong><i>NOT</i></strong> TO EXPECT ?</u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No cheap jumpscares and loud saturated noises</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No key to doors and random puzzles to solve</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No narrative that holds your hand</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not a driving game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/88dc99d24f26ab72fb8314d3be377271.poster.avif?t=1771938147\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/88dc99d24f26ab72fb8314d3be377271.webm?t=1771938147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/88dc99d24f26ab72fb8314d3be377271.mp4?t=1771938147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">IMMERSIVE SHORT HORROR EXPERIENCE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic environments in a surreal setting. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are soaked wet, and can barely see. The thunder strikes in the distance, revealing otherworldly creatures in the storm's vanishing light... </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rain has brought something else. You are not alone.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/7242443f8d3fabf29f989a6b131b8756.poster.avif?t=1771938147\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/7242443f8d3fabf29f989a6b131b8756.webm?t=1771938147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/7242443f8d3fabf29f989a6b131b8756.mp4?t=1771938147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">OTHERWORLDLY DANGERS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are creatures that can be only seen when the storm strikes. Remember where they are to avoid them.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A writhing, radiant orb of light is passing through. Look away from its draining warmth.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The forest is full of crawling nightmares. You can hear them, but can you see them in time ?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A giant absurd manifestation is towering over the trees, Start running now and you might make it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/ab7f0f1b300092b9e1440d3a53714bef.poster.avif?t=1771938147\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/ab7f0f1b300092b9e1440d3a53714bef.webm?t=1771938147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304580/extras/ab7f0f1b300092b9e1440d3a53714bef.mp4?t=1771938147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">HIGH QUALITY ENVIRONMENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a short psychological experience packed with high fidelity graphics and optimized worlds made available by Unreal Engine 5. Go through a rural ruined parking, a subterrean surreal backroom, a boggy pine forest, a dump, a tribal village, and a continuous, endless skybridge at night, away from everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
